    "content": "<div class='box'>&lt;서술형2&gt; \\\\(x = \\\\frac{1}{\\\\sqrt{5}-2}, y = \\\\frac{1}{2-\\\\sqrt{3}}\\\\) 일 때, \\\\(x-y\\\\)의 값을 구하여라.(6점)</div>",
