    "solution": "\\\\(x = \\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{5}+2}{(\\\\sqrt{5}-2)(\\\\sqrt{5}+2)} = \\\\sqrt{5}+2\\\\) \\\\\\\\ \\\\(y = \\\\frac{2+\\\\sqrt{3}}{(2-\\\\sqrt{3})(2+\\\\sqrt{3})} = 2+\\\\sqrt{3}\\\\) \\\\\\\\ \\\\(x-y = \\\\sqrt{5}+2 - (2+\\\\sqrt{3}) = \\\\sqrt{5}-\\\\sqrt{3}\\\\)"
